rem Cryogenics Lab
rem 8/22/2017

items cryotubes
items mainframe computer

do Examine Lab
 [
  ifflag test cryotubes
   [ 
     print The lab is in a state of chaos. Dead scientists fall apart before your
     print eyes. Interns flee, trying to get out before anything else explodes.
   |
    ifflag cycle system
     [
      print The lab's large cylindrical tubes are open, revealing strange hybrid 
      print creatures. An alarm sounds through out the building. Scientists that 
      print aren't helping the creatures leave.    
     |
      print The lab is full of large cylindrical tubes, connected to high pressure hoses
      print and mainframe super computers. Scientists watch the tube's gauges, recording
      print information on company devices.
     ]
   ]
 ]

ifflag cycle system
 [
  do Examine Creature
   [
    print Strange hyrib creatures, about a thrid of a meter long, have fallen out of the
    print cryotubes that suspended their life. Scientist try to help, but there's little
    print they can do.
   ]
 |]

do Exit Lab
 [
  ifflag hosaka alarm
   [
    print You leave the lab with the alarm sounding through out the building.
   |
    print You leave the lab.
   ]
  go Hosaka South
 ]



